            p
              a.observable.no-under(href='https://www.nirandfar.com/hooked' target='_blank') Hooked, by Nir Eyal
            p.m-b-3-xs
              a.observable.no-under(href='https://www.amazon.com/Designing-Behavior-Change-Psychology-Behavioral/dp/1449367623' target='_blank') Designing for Behavior Change, by Stephen Wendel            
